```python id=bloq
from qualtran.bloqs.mcmt import MultiControlX
bloq = MultiControlX(cvs=(1,) * 7)
```
```python id=golden
import numpy as np
# c7x: control=first 7 qubits (MSB), target=last (big-endian). flip target iff all controls 1.
golden = np.zeros((1<<8, 1<<8), dtype=complex)
for s in range(1<<8):
    o = (s ^ 1) if (s >> 1) == ((1<<7) - 1) else s
    golden[o, s] = 1
```
